50|$|Kellogg is the {{controlling}} shareholder of IAT Reinsurance Co. which has received media {{attention in the}} past for its former use of a U.S. law <b>exempting</b> small insurance <b>companies</b> from paying federal tax. Congress <b>exempted</b> insurance <b>companies</b> from taxes if they collected less than $350,000 in annual premiums; IAT qualified for this exemption at one time.|$|R
